-- Insert a test client with correct column names
INSERT INTO clients (userId, firstName, lastName, drivingLicenseNumber, licenseIssueDate, licenseExpiryDate, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 
  (SELECT id FROM users LIMIT 1),
  'John',
  'Doe',
  'DL123456',
  '2020-01-01',
  '2028-01-01',
  NOW(),
  NOW();

-- Insert a test contract
INSERT INTO rentalContracts (
  userId, vehicleId, clientId, clientFirstName, clientLastName, drivingLicenseNumber,
  licenseExpiryDate, rentalStartDate, rentalEndDate, rentalDays, dailyRate, totalAmount,
  discount, finalAmount, contractNumber, pickupKm, fuelLevel, status, createdAt, updatedAt
)
SELECT 
  (SELECT id FROM users LIMIT 1),
  (SELECT id FROM vehicles LIMIT 1),
  (SELECT id FROM clients WHERE drivingLicenseNumber = 'DL123456' LIMIT 1),
  'John',
  'Doe',
  'DL123456',
  '2028-01-01',
  '2026-02-13',
  '2026-02-28',
  15,
  20,
  300,
  0,
  300,
  CONCAT('CNT-', LPAD(FLOOR(RAND() * 100000), 5, '0')),
  5000,
  'Full',
  'active',
  NOW(),
  NOW();
